To build the real firmware:
1. Open the esp32-firmware project in VS Code with ESP-IDF extension
2. Set the device type in sdkconfig: CONFIG_YKP_DEVICE_TYPE_SENSOR=y
3. Run: idf.py build
4. Find the binary at: build/ykp_sensor.bin
5. Copy it here and rename to ykp_sensor_v1.2.1.bin
